name: Free Colour
description: Welcome to a world of sheer independence and indifference, where what you do and what you donâ€™t is of no concern to others. However, what you wear is of prime importance, for the people of Harajuku have keen eyes that assess you from what covers your body. To the Harajuku, what you wear stands as a defiance to the conventions and strict societal rules that have been forced upon the human world, making your ability to rebel the sole reason for your existence. With the following curation, you embark on a journey of rebellion and insurgence, placing your first mark against the demons of rules and conventions that have haunted the world of Harajuku.
